[49m[38;5;10m+    197[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ## General Architecture Pattern
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    198[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    199[0m:[38;5;10m[49m A healthcare care coordination assistant decomposes into eleven logical stages: enrollment and consent, longitudinal-and-episode-store initialization, episode lifecycle management, channel entry with disclosure, input safety screening with continuous crisis screening, identity-and-context loading with episode and federated-state retrieval, conversation handling with playbook-grounded responses and tool-mediated multi-system queries, output safety screening with operational-grounding verification, closed-loop tracking and follow-up scheduling, multi-audience visibility with consent enforcement, and audit logging with care-coordination-specific retention discipline. The cross-cutting concerns from recipes 11.1 through 11.8 carry forward; this recipe adds six new ones (episode-state-machine engine, multi-organization federated-state integration, closed-loop tracking subsystem, consent-gated multi-audience visibility, care-manager workflow integration, and document-extraction support as routine input modality).
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    200[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    201[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    202[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── ENROLLMENT + CONSENT ──────────────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    203[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    204[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient enrolls via institution app, payer benefits    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    205[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    portal, post-discharge transitional-care enrollment,   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    206[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    chronic-care-management billable enrollment, or        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    207[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    care-manager-driven enrollment]                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    208[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Documented consent specific to care-coordination     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    209[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      bot interaction with legal-counsel-reviewed language │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    210[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Explicit non-clinician disclosure acknowledged       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    211[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Explicit non-care-manager disclosure                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    212[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Multi-organization data-flow consent collected per   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    213[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      organization (where the patient receives care from   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    214[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      organizations that are not the institution operating │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    215[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      the bot)                                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    216[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Caregiver-designation consent collected separately   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    217[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      and revocably, with named caregivers and per-        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    218[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      caregiver scope                                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    219[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-team-sharing consent collected per organization │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    220[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      with specific shareable categories                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    221[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - State-specific privacy variations enforced where     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    222[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      relevant (mental-health records, substance-use under │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    223[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      42 CFR Part 2, HIV, genetic, minor-treatment)        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    224[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    225[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    226[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: signed consent record; enrollment confirmation;│
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    227[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    initialization of longitudinal and episode stores]     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    228[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    229[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    230[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    231[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── LONGITUDINAL + EPISODE STORE INITIALIZATION ───┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    232[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    233[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient longitudinal store]                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    234[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active conditions on the problem list (across        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    235[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      organizations, federated)                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    236[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active medications                                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    237[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Allergies                                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    238[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active care team across organizations                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    239[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Caregiver designations with scopes                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    240[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Stated patient preferences (preferred name, language,│
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    241[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      pronouns, channel preferences, engagement intensity, │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    242[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      quiet hours, topics off-limits)                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    243[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recent encounter summaries                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    244[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active care plans                                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    245[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Conversation history                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    246[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Consent posture per organization, per category, per  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    247[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      caregiver                                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    248[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    249[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Per-episode store]                                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    250[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Episode_id, episode_type, status, start, expected    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    251[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      end, exit conditions                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    252[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Episode-specific playbook reference                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    253[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Operational items list with status and next-action   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    254[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Responsible parties per item                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    255[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Closed-loop-tracking pointers                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    256[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-manager assignment (where applicable)           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    257[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    258[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    259[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: longitudinal and episode stores ready for      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    260[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    coordination conversations]                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    261[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    262[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    263[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    264[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── EPISODE LIFECYCLE MANAGEMENT ──────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    265[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    266[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Episode initiation triggers]                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    267[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - ADT discharge event from hospital EHR                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    268[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Referral order from any integrated EHR              │
