[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    514[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      item status                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    515[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Event-driven updates from inbound HL7 v2 ADT, FHIR   │
