[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    532[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: continuously updated tracking state; follow-up │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    533[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    actions scheduled; care-manager escalations queued]    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    534[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
