[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    580[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active playbook-corpus version                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    581[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active episode-state version                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    582[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Final disposition                                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    583[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    584[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Care-coordination-specific retention]                  │
